2012: Played in eight Web.com Tour events, making six cuts. Opened the season with a T18 at the South Georgia Classic in Valdosta.  2009: Played in two Web.com Tour events. Missed the cut at both the Knoxville Open and the Preferred Health Systems Wichita Open.
